member.example:
This sample shows how to call IncrementCountAsync.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
SimplePostClient client = new SimplePostClient(endpoint);

Response<int> response = await client.IncrementCountAsync(1234);

This sample shows how to call IncrementCountAsync with all parameters.

